# Alembic Migrations for Resync

## First-time setup
```bash
# Apply all migrations to a fresh database
alembic upgrade head

# Or let the application create tables automatically on first startup
# (via initialize_database() called from wiring.py)
```

## Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add_user_preferences_table"
```

## Rollback
```bash
alembic downgrade -1          # one step back
alembic downgrade base        # all the way back
```
